author: Lauren Murphy
title: MusicNews | Puff Daddy releases brand new song 'Workin'' - hear it now
text:
Puff Daddy has revealed a brand new song online after debuting it live at the B.E.T. Awards on Tuesday night.
It's called ' Workin' and as the title suggests, it sees the rapper bigging-up his work ethic while also giving a number of shout-outs to the late Notorious B.I.G.
